data.eml:eml: The fourth Bent-toed Gecko of the genus Cyrtodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Java, Indonesia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Riyanto, Awal, Grismer, L. Lee, Wood, Perry L. (2015): The fourth Bent-toed Gecko of the genus Cyrtodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Java, Indonesia. Zootaxa 4059 (2): 351-363, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4059.2.6
